{"tid":1334660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"孫子兵法有云","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:45:39.000Z","uid":282202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4cccccba10fc1167830bc978611b66f374a58c","tid":1334660,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之。攻其無備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。<br />\n<br />\n佢放哂水馬在狗屋，政總。示威者仲衝呢d 位咪蝕底，攻其無備，出其不意先得。集思廣益一下，甚至聽日一完就散水，佢真係會估我地唔到。"},{"pid":"84efe705a19b49584982b9d2fdec2c61abf1edd0","tid":1334660,"uid":254536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dddae439334da98c372b0ff7b7c7e02400ca8d6d","tid":1334660,"uid":30163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:49:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5247ce7ea738966193b9273fe4789ea231ab1c6c","tid":1334660,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"80f4f26c2bdbed699fd783ec0cd8671baf14ed29","tid":1334660,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}